column16: A.  J.   Reed pops out to third baseman Trevor Plouffe in foul territory.
Derek Fisher doubles (1) on a sharp line drive to center fielder Peter Bourjos.   Jake Marisnick scores.
Jake Marisnick doubles (7) on a line drive to center fielder Peter Bourjos.   Alex Bregman scores.

Alex Bregman walks.   Carlos Beltran to 2nd.
